"Why," they say, "we heard you were the people that did not believe in conversion, and here you are talking to me about conversion, you are appealing to me on conversion." And all that prejudice is swept away then you talk to individuals in that way. But there is strength exhausted at our camp-meetings that need not be; 


                     -38- 

because we can have constant help from God, and be strengthened all the time.
